                </div2>

                <div2 source="#Paris_1692_7 #Paris_1690_5" n="53">
                    <p><g ref="#fr_pieds_de_mouche"/>Il semble que le <app>
                            <rdg wit="#Paris_1690_5">Roman</rdg>
                            <rdg wit="#Paris_1692_7">roman</rdg>
